    "The case study and user study demonstrate that HINTs effectively supports the sensemaking of a corpus.",
    "We attribute this outcome to a good model alignment and a combined usage of LLM as a general NLP task solver and intelligent agent.",
    "Still, there are some limitations to the current approach.",
    "First, designing prompts for domain-specific use cases is a time-consuming trial-and-error process.",
    "There is currently a lack of effective evaluation methods for these customized extraction tasks, so the evaluation of the effectiveness of the extraction pipeline relies on human judgment."
